  <h3>What Makes This Retreat Different</h3>
  <p>Unlike many wellness retreats focused on relaxation alone, Varsha offers a trauma-informed therapeutic approach rooted in Compassionate Inquiry®, developed by Dr Gabor Maté.</p>
